{"product_id":"clarifying-solid-shampoo-with-rhubarb-extract","title":"Magrada Clarifying Solid Shampoo With Rhubarb Extract 58g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAn eco-friendly alternative to classical shampoos. Thanks to its concentrated formula, the solid shampoo will last longer, and its packaging is made of recycled aluminium.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo enriched with rhubarb extract strengthens hair, helps remove flaking skin from the scalp, prevents scalp irritation, and gives the hair an extraordinary shine. The shampoo also helps to deep-clean the hair and scalp from oils, sweat, and product residue. This results in lovely clean hair, scented with juicy red rhubarb.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo is ideal for women, men, and children for daily use and is also suitable for sensitive and delicate scalps.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eRhubarb root extract\u003c\/span\u003e has anti-inflammatory and anti-bacterial properties and it helps sooth a sensitive and irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e contains plenty of essential fatty acids, which help to improve the protective function of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eRub the shampoo in your hands until a lather forms and apply directly on wet hair. Massage the shampoo on the scalp, then rinse. After use, leave the shampoo in a dry place to set until the next time you wash your hair.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sodium Coco-Sulfate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate, Parfum, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Rheum Palmatum (Rhubarb) Root Extract, Polyquaternium-7, Aqua, Panthenol, Distearoylethyl Dimonium Chloride.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 97%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e SLS-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927718834503,"sku":"","price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-clarifying-solid-shampoo-with-rhubarb-extract-58g-486824.png?v=1739897405","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/clarifying-solid-shampoo-with-rhubarb-extract","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}